{"title":"Visual Basic 练习2019题(第三场)","uid":"fa806be830d9a3c6ced3c4d20a53813e","slug":"g","date":"2024-01-07T00:00:00.000Z","updated":"2024-10-27T03:44:11.120Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/g.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/IMG/g/1.png","content":"<ul>\n<li>本网站严格遵守<a href=\"https://fiung.com/\">《Fiung community 通用管理办法》</a></li>\n<li>投诉<a href=\"https://fiung.com/\">点击这里</a></li>\n<li>校验码: g</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"/./IMG/g/1.png\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"第三场\"><a href=\"#第三场\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"第三场\"></a>第三场</h1><h2 id=\"第一题\"><a href=\"#第一题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"第一题\"></a>第一题</h2><p>选中单选按钮好，单击确定按钮，在文本框中显示一个随机生成的 65-90 的整数，<br>并在标签中连续显示这么多个“好”，选中字符按钮，单击确定按钮，则在标签中显示<br>这个随机数所转换的字符。不得使用循环<br><img src=\"/./IMG/g/1.png\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Private Sub Command1_Click()</span><br><span class=\"line\">Text1.Text = Int(Rnd * 26 + 65)</span><br><span class=\"line\">n = Val(Text1.Text)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">If Option1 Then</span><br><span class=\"line\"> Label1.Caption = String(n, &quot;好&quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">End If</span><br><span class=\"line\"> If Option2 Then</span><br><span class=\"line\">  Label1.Caption = Chr(n)</span><br><span class=\"line\">End If</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">End Sub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"第二题\"><a href=\"#第二题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"第二题\"></a>第二题</h2><p>单击按钮后在文本框中随机生成 10 个 3 位数，中间用空格隔开，并在标签中显示出<br>最大的数<br><img src=\"/./IMG/g/2.png\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Private Sub Command1_Click()</span><br><span class=\"line\">Dim a(1 To 10)</span><br><span class=\"line\">For i = 1 To 10</span><br><span class=\"line\">Randomize</span><br><span class=\"line\">a(i) = Int(Rnd * 900 + 100)</span><br><span class=\"line\">f = f &amp; a(i) &amp; &quot; &quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">If m &lt; a(i) Then m = a(i)</span><br><span class=\"line\">Next i</span><br><span class=\"line\">Text1 = f</span><br><span class=\"line\">Label1 = &quot;十个数中最大的数是&quot; &amp; m</span><br><span class=\"line\">End Sub</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"第三题\"><a href=\"#第三题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"第三题\"></a>第三题</h2><p>在文本框中输入一个 1-20 的数字，生成 n 行 n 列的矩阵，要求矩阵下半部分为 1，其他<br>为 0，点击显示按钮将其打印出来。（双重循环）<br><img src=\"/./IMG/g/3.png\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Dim a(20, 20)</span><br><span class=\"line\">Private Sub Command1_Click()</span><br><span class=\"line\">Cls</span><br><span class=\"line\">z = Val(Text1)</span><br><span class=\"line\">For y = 1 To z</span><br><span class=\"line\">For x = 1 To z</span><br><span class=\"line\">If x &gt; y Then</span><br><span class=\"line\">  Print &quot;0 &quot;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  Else</span><br><span class=\"line\">  Print &quot;1 &quot;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   End If</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">   Next x</span><br><span class=\"line\">   Print</span><br><span class=\"line\">   Next y</span><br><span class=\"line\">End Sub</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"第四题\"><a href=\"#第四题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"第四题\"></a>第四题</h2><p>分别单击 0 按钮和 1 按钮，再单击统计并输出按钮，则在 label 中显示相对应得二进制<br>数，并统计 0 的个数和 1 的个数。单击初始化按钮则所有都还原，label 清空。单击退出则<br>退出。<br><img src=\"/./IMG/g/4.png\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Dim c, i, f</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Private Sub Command1_Click()</span><br><span class=\"line\">a = &quot;0&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">i = i + 1</span><br><span class=\"line\">c = c &amp; a</span><br><span class=\"line\">End Sub</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Private Sub Command2_Click()</span><br><span class=\"line\">b = &quot;1&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">f = f + 1</span><br><span class=\"line\">c = c &amp; b</span><br><span class=\"line\">End Sub</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Private Sub Command3_Click()</span><br><span class=\"line\">Label1 = &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">c = &quot;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">f = 0</span><br><span class=\"line\">i = 0</span><br><span class=\"line\">End Sub</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Private Sub Command4_Click()</span><br><span class=\"line\">End</span><br><span class=\"line\">End Sub</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Private Sub Command5_Click()</span><br><span class=\"line\">Label1 = &quot;这个二进制是&quot; &amp; c &amp; vbCrLf &amp; &quot;这个数中的零的个数是&quot; &amp; i &amp; &quot; 这个数中的一的个数是&quot; &amp; f</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">End Sub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","text":" 本网站严格遵守《Fiung community 通用管理办法》 投诉点击这里 校验码: g 第三场第一题选中单选按钮好，单击确定按钮，在文本框中显示一个随机生...","permalink":"/post/g","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.5k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%9C%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第三场</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a c